These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, snake, rat, hedgehog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, rugby, tennis
1. the owner of the rat is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is rowing##2
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
3. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
4. the person who's sport is rowing is not the owner of the rat##6
5. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
6. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Pet   | hedgehog  | goldfish | rat | snake  |
| Sport   | biathlon | rugby   | tennis  | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, tomato, watermelon, zucchini
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, weightlifting, skateboarding, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##8
2. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the right of the person eating zucchini##5
3. the person eating grapes is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person eating zucchini is between the person eating grapes and the person eating tomato##2
5. the person eating tomato is somewhere between the person eating watermelon and the person who's sport is climbing##7
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5
7. the person who's sport is climbing is not to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | watermelon | tomato          | zucchini | grapes     |
| Sport    | skateboarding      | biathlon | climbing | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, electrician, nurse, paramedic
4 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, mah-jongg, canasta
1. the person playing billiard is not to the left of the nurse##8
2. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
3. the electrician is on the right of the bartender##1
4. the electrician is in an even position##4
5. the paramedic is on the far left or far right##3
6. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5
7. the paramedic is the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | bartender | electrician | nurse     | paramedic |
| Game   | backgammon    | canasta   | billiard | mah-jongg    |

