.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, disco, metal, rock
City: marseilles, paris, colone, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the left of the person traveling to paris##8
3. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the fan of disco##1
4. the fan of rock is not to the right of the person traveling to colone##8
5. the fan of blues is the person traveling to marseilles##1
6. the fan of blues is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
7. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | disco         | rock   | blues    |
| City         | paris | edinburgh | colone | marseilles |

