.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, family, romance, scientific
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, cherry, pear, mango
1. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching epic movies and the person watching family movies##7
2. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating pear##5
3. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching romance movies and the person watching epic movies##7
4. the person watching romance movies is not to the left of the person eating mango##8
5. the person eating mango is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the person eating cherry##7
6. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the right of the person watching scientific movies##5
7. the person eating cherry is not to the left of the person watching epic movies##8
8. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | family   | romance | scientific | epic    |
| Food         | nectarine | mango   | pear   | cherry |

