.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, kiwi, lettuce, pineapple
There are 4 different nationalities: british, french, dutch, pakistani
1. the pakistani is on the left of the dutch##1
2. the french is somewhere to the left of the person eating cauliflower##5
3. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the dutch##1
4. the british is on the left or right of the dutch##3
5. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the left of the person eating kiwi##5
6. the person eating pineapple is not to the left of the french##8
7. the person eating pineapple is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | pineapple | cauliflower | kiwi  | lettuce |
| Nationality   | french   | pakistani         | dutch | british |

