.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, dressmaker, entrepreneur, project-manager
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, juice, mirinda, almond-milk
1. the entrepreneur is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
2. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
3. the dressmaker is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the dressmaker##7
5. the entrepreneur is not to the right of the project-manager##8
6. the project-manager is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the entrepreneur##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Job     | dressmaker | entrepreneur | project-manager | doctor     |
| Beverage   | sprite   | mirinda        | almond-milk          | juice |

