3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
4. the person who growsrose is not to the right of the person who growssunflower##8
5. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
