.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, snake, turtle, goldfish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, ice-hockey, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##8
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the owner of the snake##7
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
8. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Pet   | goldfish | snake         | turtle    | chinchilla       |
| Sport      | handball | skateboarding | biathlon | ice-hockey |

