.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, sprite, tea
House: ranch-style, colonial, cottage, townhouse
1. the townhouse house is not to the left of the colonial house##8
2. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
3. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking tea and the cottage house##2
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
6. the ranch-style house is between the colonial house and the townhouse house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Beverage   | 7up     | almond-milk | tea        | sprite       |
| House      | cottage | colonial  | ranch-style | townhouse |

