.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, airplane, bike, quad-bike
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, family, superhero
 1. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching family movies##5
 2. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
 3. the person driving the ship is the person watching family movies##1
 4. the person watching family movies is not to the right of the person watching crime movies##8
 5. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 6. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
 7. the person watching crime movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person driving the ship is not to the right of the person watching family movies##8
 9. the person watching crime movies is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
10. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the person watching adventure movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Transport          | airplane    | bike | ship | quad-bike |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | superhero  | family     | crime    |

