2. the person eating grapefruit is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
3. the person playing whist is the person playing whist##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is the person eating peas##1
5. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
6. the person eating avocado is between the person playing whist and the person eating peas##2
7. the person eating grapefruit is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food    | peas        | avocado | asparagus | grapefruit |
| Game   | mah-jongg | canasta | whist   | go    |

