.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, hamster, hedgehog
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, pink, black, fuchsia
1. the person who likes pink is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
2. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##8
4. the owner of the hamster is the person who likes brown##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the person who likes pink and the person who likes brown##7
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the person who likes black is between the person who likes fuchsia and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | frog    | hedgehog | chinchilla | hamster |
| Color   | pink | fuchsia      | black     | brown     |

 